Sentencas: Very high electrical conductivity of similar to 0.021 S/cm at 600 degrees C is obtained in Ce0.79Gd0.20Co0.01O2-delta.
Titulo: Enhanced electrical conductivity in Ce0.79Gd0.20Co0.01O2-δ for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Corresponding activation energy of conduction similar to 0.43 eV measured in the temperature range of 400-700 degrees C is found to be notably low.
Titulo: Enhanced electrical conductivity in Ce0.79Gd0.20Co0.01O2-δ for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Improved electrical properties with 99% of the theoretical density as obtained for these specimens, prepared using powder of average particle size similar to 20 nm and subsequent sintering at 1100 degrees C, is considered to be a significant step to reduce the processing temperature.
Titulo: Enhanced electrical conductivity in Ce0.79Gd0.20Co0.01O2-δ for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The measured electrical potential of similar to 1 V indicates the suitability of its use as an electrolyte in electrochemical devices.
Titulo: Enhanced electrical conductivity in Ce0.79Gd0.20Co0.01O2-δ for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications
